Gems
====

- https://github.com/itamae-kitchen
  https://itamae.kitchen/
  Configuration management tool inspired by Chef, but simpler and lightweight.
- https://github.com/itamae-kitchen/mitamae
  -> mruby version

- https://github.com/k0kubun/itamae-template
  Itamae template generator for roles and cookbooks

- https://github.com/sorah/hocho
  Hocho: an itamae wrapper
  -> remote itamae local support on rsync+bundler

- https://serverspec.org/
  https://github.com/mizzy/serverspec
  RSpec tests for your servers configured by CFEngine, Puppet, Ansible,
  Itamae or anything else. (Gosuke Miyashita)
  Comparison with inspec:
  - https://medium.com/@Joachim8675309/serverspec-vs-inspec-17272df2718f
  - https://www.inspec.io/docs/reference/migration/
  - https://www.inspec.io/docs/reference/inspec_and_friends/

- https://github.com/mizzy/specinfra/
  Command Execution Framework for serverspec, itamae and so on http://serverspec.org/
